https://stackoverflow.com/questions/33696944/how-do-i-enable-remote-access-request-in-elasticsearch-2-0
configure the config file
example:
for elasticsearch:
sudo nano etc/elasticsearch/elasticsearch.yml
make netowrk.host : 0.0.0.0
ssh to your device
suod ufw allow from <remote_server_ip> to any prot <localhost_port>
curl -X GET http://localhost:9200 to get the test response
